article_node.title: Trista and Ryan Sutter's 2 Kids Look All Grown Up on the First Day of Junior and Senior Year
article_node.summary: Former "Bachelorette" star Trista Sutter posted an emotional Instagram Reel on Aug. 14 celebrating her daughter Blakeley's first day of junior year and son Maxwell's first day of senior year, reflecting on how quickly time passes. The clip compiled photos from their first days of school each year, ending with a sweet moment of the siblings together. Sutter also shared a pet‑peeve about parents at kids' sports games, insisting they sit on their team’s side, and has previously posted family photos for Easter and other milestones. The article highlights her gratitude for family and her ongoing engagement with fans through social media.
